## Tables

### Create a table with columns
```bash
curl -s -X POST "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/tables" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "posts",
    "columns": [
      { "name": "title",   "type": "VARCHAR(255)", "nullable": false },
      { "name": "body",    "type": "TEXT",         "nullable": true  },
      { "name": "user_id", "type": "INT",          "nullable": false }
    ]
  }'
```

### Allowed column types
`INT` `BIGINT` `VARCHAR(255)` `TEXT` `BOOLEAN` `DATETIME` `DECIMAL(10,2)` `FLOAT`

### List tables
```bash
curl -s "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/tables" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN"
```

### Delete a table
```bash
curl -s -X DELETE "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/tables/posts" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN"
```

